text: Oh Long Johnson is a 2019 album by Spanish pop group Miss Caffeina. ==Background== The title of the album was inspired by the famous viral video of the Oh Long Johnson cat.Betevé - Miss Caffeina, del mem a , ConvictOh Long Johnson’20 minutos, 25.07.2019 - Miss Caffeina cumplirá en el Low 40 conciertos de Oh Long Johnson: "Nuestra mejor gira, estamos más unidos que nunca" The album was produced by British producer, Max Dingel.El Mundo, 18 mar. 2019 - Disco/ Oh Long Johnson, Miss Caffeina: Elegante consolidación - DAVID SAAVEDRA ==Chart performance== The album was in the Spanish charts for ten weeks, peaking at No. 1 in March 2019.Acharts.co - Oh Long Johnson, HISTORIC PERFORMANCE, Spain Albums Top 100Trendencias, 17 Marzo 2019 - Charlamos con Miss Caffeina sobre su disco 'Oh Long Johnson' (y descubrimos el significado de su título) ==Track listing== {| class="wikitable plainrowheaders sortable" |- !
